Use generate_residual_solvent.js as the renderer/template reference for the Residual Solvent report structure. The approved document will not be uploaded at runtime. The JS file defines the intended section order, payload structure, residual-solvent nested table layout, supplier declaration table, product details table, composition table, conclusion sections, references, annexure list, revision history, and signatures. However, do not treat the JS as the backend calculation logic. Build separate residual-solvent Excel parsing, annexure conversion, mapping, calculation, and validation logic in app.py/modules, then pass a clean payload into this renderer.
###
Before finalizing, remove EI bleed and hardcoding:
- Do not use EI element/PDE/30% PDE logic.
- Convert hardcoded Esomeprazole section titles into dynamic product metadata.
